Thai cabinet to decide on zero - coupon bond issue . Thailand ' s cabinet is expected to approve a total zero - coupon bond issue of 50 billion baht on Tuesday , Bank of Thailand governor Rerngchai Marakanond said on Monday . But the actual issue will be divided into tranches with the first lot of 500 million baht expected to be launched later in the week , he said . The bonds are being planned by the authorities to raise funds to help cash - strapped firms in the currently depressed property sector . MORE ak / ram 
